name: Eclipse, the Cosmic Harbinger
text: Beneath an eternal twilight, Eclipse emerged, an omen woven from the night's tapestry. Its wings unfurled, dusted with stardust, fluttering silently. Villagers whispered of its arrival, the harbinger of change—some saying renewal, others, ruin. Yet, as stars mirrored in its gaze, Eclipse remained an enigma, aloof and untouched.
